  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW YOUR MOVIES?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your knowledge across some of the most popular movie genres of all time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Movie Trivia Challenge has never been so much fun. Challenge yourself in Single Player, or host a movie trivia night with friends and family in Party Mode (up to 4 players). Choose a category, answer thousands of multiple-choice questions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Includes 9 fan-favorite categories:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Comedy</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sci‑Fi</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horror</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Romance</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Foreign</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kids</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>General</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2010‑Present</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Player Mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Mode (Up to 4 Players)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thousands of multiple-choice questions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for group trivia nights</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick, pick-up-and-play sessions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Family-friendly fun for all ages</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gamepad support</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for? Download now and get your brain ready for The Movie Trivia Challenge!</p>",
